Six lucky Kenyans will get a chance to watch one of the Formula 1 Grand Prix races anywhere in the world, thanks to an ongoing Kenya Breweries Ltd (KBL) promo. The winners in the 12-week promo dubbed ‘Experience Formula 1 with Johnnie Walker’, the KBL head of spirits, AnnJoy Muhoro, said in a statement, would also enjoy access to the Johnnie Walker VIP hospitality tent. ALSO READ:

Daniel Ricciardo wins Chinese Grand Prix beating Lewis Hamilton and Sebastian Vettel 